report.title: Not Worth It
report.author: Yowza
report.bodytext: Yuck. Tastes horrible and it gets stuck in your throat. Tough time getting it out, like that oily-gasoline taste, really nasty. The come down is awful. Shaky, nervous, totally twitched-out. Don't waste your money. It's really aggravating. /n /n [Reported Dose: '1g']
